Header.title: Introduction to Data Science
Header.paragraph: Enhance your skills in Data Science to grow yourself, be knowledgeable and efficient enough to get recognised in any industry.

About.paragraph: Tensor is a strong advanced digital platform. It is an initiative by Lejhro to provide advanced educational facilities for the upcoming generation, professionals and entrepreneurs who will be entering the corporate world. We have provided our support to various types of small and medium enterprises to upgrade their employees through training in different technological courses such as Full Stack Development, Data Sciences, Product Engineering and many other different courses with the help of the best industry experts.
